item.title: How can i fix this?
item.dc:creator: @Mod_Adam Adam
item.description:
@Mod_Adam wrote:

Moving a bracket one space over in either direction is not a legitimate error. This error is telling the user that a new one is expected. Or there could be one too many. Try matching your brackets with each other like so:

public static void main(String[] args) [b]{[/b] // Open #1 for(int fake loop, pay no attention) [b]{[/b] // Open #2 System.out.print( "Hai." ); [b]}[/b] // Close #2 [b]}[/b] // Close #1

See in that code I have 2 { brackets, therefore, I need to counter them with 2 } brackets. Make sure you open and close the same amount of times.
